  m_Name: CommanderEvent
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WarForOilEvent
  id: wfo_wtetwc_03
  displayName: A Commander Wants to End the War
  description: One of the senior commanders argues that the war is no longer sustainable.
    He begins seeking internal military support for initiating peace negotiations.
  devNote: "mafya skilli olu\u015Fturulunca \xF6ld\xFCrme choice una eklenecek"
  eventNote: "bu event de wants to end the war conceptinin kolay olan\u0131d\u0131r.
    sava\u015F\u0131 bitirmek isteyen komutand\u0131r ancak di\u011Fer ikisine g\xF6re
    k\xFC\xE7\xFCk birka\xE7 mekanik farkl\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131 var\n\nikna etme
    choice u yine var ve ikna etme \u015Fans\u0131n y\xFCksek\n\nbar\u0131\u015F\u0131
    destekleme se\xE7ene\u011Fi yine var ancak bu sefer kesin etkili de\u011Fil,
    b\xFCy\xFCk olas\u0131l\u0131kla bitirir \xE7\xFCnk\xFC komutan + bizim sava\u015F\u0131
    bitirme iste\u011Fimiz \xFCst\xFC o kadar ba\u011Flamak zorunda de\u011Fil.\n\n\xF6ld\xFCrme
    se\xE7ene\u011Fi yine var o da %10 artt\u0131r\u0131r protest ba\u015Flama olas\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131\n"
